    public abstract class GeoWaveWritableInputMapper<KEYOUT,VALUEOUT>
extends org.apache.hadoop.mapreduce.Mapper<GeoWaveInputKey,org.apache.hadoop.io.ObjectWritable,KEYOUT,VALUEOUT>
    This abstract class can be extended by GeoWave analytics. It handles the conversion of native GeoWave objects into objects that are writable. It is a mapper that converts to writable objects for the input. This conversion will only work if the data adapter implements HadoopDataAdapter.
